[23]Subsequently pilgrimages took place at irregular intervals to view the garment: 1513, 1514, 1515, 1516, 1517, 1524, 1531, 1538, 1545, 1655, 1810, 1844, 1891, 1933, 1959, 1996.
[25]The last exhibition of the tunic, in 1996, was seen by over one million pilgrims and visitors.
